Web services:
web services : a software system designed to support interoperable machine - to machine interaction over a netwrork
API - application programmer interface
apis speacify how software components should interact with one and another.
Services module : Services modules allows drupal to expose its data and internal actions to other applications via the web services api
Requests and Responses : Drupal gets the requests from the external services and send the response through the api. The requested is iniated using rest or xmlrpc.
Drupal 's data & actions : data can be nodes, users, comments, views etc. actions can be authenticate a user, create a node, trigger password and reset email.

